dcterms:description: The eICU Collaborative Research Database v1.2 was used for all experiments described in this paper. It consists of 94 time series variables including periodic and aperiodic vital signs and irregularly measured lab tests, extracted from a cohort of 20,878 patients with 72-720 hours of history, extending from ICU admission to dispatch.
dcterms:title: eICU Collaborative Research Database v1.2
